name: Blythe : Hello Harvest (never been removed from box)
description:
Neo Blythe Hello Harvest. Produced by CWC Takara (2007)

Type : RBL
Size : Neo Blythe 12 inches

Personally I think Hello Harvest is one of the best dolls for both keeping as original as well as custom. Her skin tone is lovely healthy and very photogenic. 

She has never been removed from her original box. 

Shipping : Via EMS 20 USD worldwide. 
Status : Ready to ship within 2 days of payment. 
Payment : Credit card and PayPal (Just follow the steps)

name: Blythe : Yuki no namida hime (never been removed from brown box)
description: Limited Edition Blythe doll designed by Baby, The Stars Shine Bright. Produced by CWC Takara (2006) Type : RBL (Radiant Blythe) Size : Neo Blythe (12 inches) I got her from the time I participated in Blythe design contest in 2007 in Japan by myself. Very rare doll. Special eye chips with the letter "B" on her pink eye. She came with original outfits and gears designed by the famous lolita brand, "Baby, The Star Shines Bright". She also has a crystal tear drop pull ring and tiara plus ski coat jacket with a pair of skis. She has never been removed from the original brown box. Therefore, the first photo of her came from other collector. Just so you get the idea of how she looks like out of the box. Shipping : Via EMS 20 USD worldwide. Status : Ready to ship within 2 days of payment. Payment : Credit card and PayPal (Just follow the steps)
